{
  "stem": "13141.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They are not looking down on us-- at least not so much any more as they used to.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I think Israel has a lot to do with this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "God forbid, if Israel wouldn't exist, I don't know what would happen again.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And even in the United States, I feel-- maybe because I have-- with the experiences I have-- I think that, sooner or later, the United States will have to go way to the right.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because, look at criminality.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Look at pollution.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Look at the poverty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Look at welfare.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We have not advanced very much, I would say, as a country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So democracy-- as I said before, I'm a US citizen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'm very proud to be a US citizen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I am very grateful to the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would do anything for the United States.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But through democracy, obviously, we have not been able to solve these problems.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There are just too many discussions, too many committees which are being formed where they don't have the answers for something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then, all of a sudden after [INAUDIBLE] died out, and you don't hear about it anymore.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I feel that somehow, to [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] win the war against criminality, against the pollution-- because there's a lot of graft going on, too, you know-- I am afraid that, to find a solution, the United States will have to move a little bit away from that free speech.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Look at all the pornography.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They, they, they cover themselves, and they get away with it with the-- with the Constitution.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They refer to the free speech and liberty.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But what is being done under this-- under this [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] name?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "What negative things are being done, day in and day out, using free speech as a cover?",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
